window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Anyone determined enough can ruin a city. The only question is: do I have what it takes to rule one?</b></p> <p>After Crescent Thorn's failed attack on Blackfall Manor, things are finally calm enough to turn my attention back to Vohra and rebuild the underworld.</p> <p>But there are no shortage of fires to put out; enough problems both near and far that my fledgling empire might be in trouble before it begins.</p> <p>The one person who can hope to stem the tide is also my single biggest threat in this world.</p> <p>Jasper Ildan, the Jackal of Vohra, is the devil I don’t know, but when my back’s against the wall, even I’ll consider making a deal.</p>"; 
